Package Pump

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Pump
    Pump class that adds, removes gas from set tanks.
    PumpDieselCommand
    Contains PumpDieselCommand which pumps diesel gas out of the diesel tank using a pump object.
    PumpDriver
    Driver class that allows the testing/running of PumpThread objects
    PumpKiosk
    PumpKiosk is a Kiosk that store gasoline prices, commands to pump gas and run() in order to complete a pump requests (meant to be used in a thread)
    PumpMidGradeCommand
    Contains PumpDieselCommand which pumps diesel gas out of the diesel tank using a pump object.
    PumpPremiumCommand
    Contains PumpDieselCommand which pumps diesel gas out of the diesel tank using a pump object.
    PumpThread
    PumpThread class that creates additional functionality needed for our threads while running a PumpKiosk
    PumpUnleadedCommand
    Contains PumpDieselCommand which pumps diesel gas out of the diesel tank using a pump object.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PumpException
    PumpException used if there is a problem when pumping gas
